FBIS4-15467 "drsov068_a_94017" FBIS-SOV-94-068 Daily Report 8 Apr 1994 RUSSIA INTERNATIONAL AFFAIRS Air Force Chief on Talks Air Force Chief on Talks MK0804065094 Moscow SEGODNYA in Russian 8 Apr 94 p 1 MK0804065094 Moscow SEGODNYA Russian BFN [Unattributed report: "Strategic Bomber Accord With Ukraine Not Reached"] [Text] Petr Deynekin, commander-in-chief of the Russian Federation Air Force, has intimated that no "mutually acceptable agreement" on the turning over to Russia of strategic bombers stationed on Ukraine's territory has been reached so far. According to him, the stumbling block at the talks is the "astronomical" sum the Ukrainian side is asking for the transfer of the bombers. Ukraine wishes to pay around 700 billion rubles of its debt to Russia in 42 aircraft. In the Russian side's view, the figure should be some 200 billion rubles.
